
To cleanly build the extension:
ant -Dextension.name=ezbrightcove clean-all build pack

To cleanly build the extension as trial edition:
ant -Dextension.name=ezbrightcove clean-all trial

To see all available options:
ant -Dextension.name=ezbrightcove -p help


Results are in the build directory.

Dependencies:
ant, ant-contrib
